long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Sorts all tabs in the current window by their URLs. The extension requests only a single permission: tabs. This is necessary to read the URL for each tab, and to assign it a new placement. Tab Defrag does nothing more.
